title: 3BR, 2BA One-Level Townhome
app_fee: $45.00; credit, background, criminal, rent bureau, employment check
posting_body: ['Address:  1184 Xene Lane N,  Plymouth  MN  55447', 'Description:  This property is professionally managed.', '   One Level Townhome in a great location.', ' Home features recent updates to the bathrooms, kitchen, appliances and flooring.', ' Master bedroom includes a walk-in closet & private master three quarter bath.', ' Two additional bedrooms with one leading into the four-season porch which overlooks a scenic pond & walks out to a patio.', 'Kitchen, dining & living room w/gas fireplace have an open concept feel & vaulted ceiling.', ' HOA offers the following amenities: outdoor pool, pickle ball court, walking/biking trails & tennis courts.', 'This property has a 2-car attached garage and is close to golf course, parks, and Parker Lake.', 'This is a NON-smoking property.', 'One small dog under 25 pounds allowed.', 'Cats need not apply.', ' Not Section 8 approved.', ' Professionally managed by Acuity Group.', 'Information:', 'Rent Rate:  $ 2,495', 'Security Deposit:  $ 2,495', 'Available:  08/15/2022', 'Sq Ft (approx):  1536', 'Parking:  2 car attached with additional concrete pad', 'Lease Terms:  Minimum 12 month lease.', ' Pets will be considered case-by-case.', ' Full background and credit check required on all tenants over 18 years.', 'If you are interested in viewing this property, please visit our website at <URL> and complete the Tenant Questionnaire.', ' Upon receipt, a leasing agent will be in touch to set up a showing.', ' Please be as complete as possible in order to avoid showing delays!', 'Property listed by Acuity Group / 564 Dodge Ave, Suite A / Elk River.']
